OL,3,CTUC calls for AI to be regulated in
OL,4,Cthe workplace
OL,6,FThe UK is losing the "race against
OL,7,Ftime" to regulate AI in the workplace,
OL,8,Funions are warning.
OL,10,FThe TUC said employment law is failing
OL,11,Fto keep pace with the rapid speed of
OL,12,Ftechnological change, leaving many
OL,13,Fworkers vulnerable to exploitation and
OL,14,Fdiscrimination.
OL,16,FThe union organisation published a
OL,17,F"ready-to-go" legal blueprint for
OL,18,Fregulating AI in the workplace, with a
OL,19,Fsuggested Bill developed in
OL,20,Fpartnership with legal experts.
