OL,3,CTUC calls for AI to be regulated in
OL,4,Cthe workplace
OL,6,FIt sets out new legal rights and
OL,7,Fprotections including a legal duty on
OL,8,Femployers to consult trade unions on
OL,9,Fthe use of high risk and intrusive
OL,10,Fforms of AI in the workplace and
OL,11,Fprotections against unfair dismissal
OL,12,Fby AI.
OL,14,FThe TUC called on all political
OL,15,Fparties to support AI regulation in
OL,16,Fthe workplace, describing it as an
OL,17,F"urgent national priority".
