OL,3,CTUC calls for AI to be regulated in
OL,4,Cthe workplace
OL,6,FAI is already making high-risk, life-
OL,7,Fchanging decisions about workers'
OL,8,Flives, such as line-managing, hiring
OL,9,Fand firing staff and is being used to
OL,10,Fanalyse facial expressions, tone of
OL,11,Fvoice and accents to assess
OL,12,Fcandidates' suitability for roles,
OL,13,Fsaid the TUC.
OL,15,FIt warned that the UK is at risk of
OL,16,Fbecoming an international outlier on
OL,17,FAI regulation, highlighting that other
OL,18,Fcountries such as the US, China,
OL,19,FCanada and those in the EU, were
OL,20,Fimplementing new laws for how AI
OL,21,Fshould be used.
