OL,3,CTUC calls for AI to be regulated in
OL,4,Cthe workplace
OL,6,FTUC assistant general secretary Kate
OL,7,FBell said: "UK employment law is
OL,8,Fsimply failing to keep pace with the
OL,9,Frapid speed of technological change.
OL,10,FWe are losing the race to regulate AI
OL,11,Fin the workplace.
OL,13,F"AI is already making life-changing
OL,14,Fcalls in the workplace, including how
OL,15,Fpeople are hired, performance managed
OL,16,Fand fired.
OL,18,F"We urgently need to put new
OL,19,Fguardrails in place to protect workers
OL,20,Ffrom exploitation and discrimination.
OL,21,FThis should be a national priority.
